<HR style="MARGIN-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN-RIGHT: 0px">

<H2>Course Projects</H2>
<H3>&nbsp;</H3>
<H3>9/2010-10/2010 (AI and GUI) Graphic Computer Game with AI Agent Design</H3>
<H3>In group of 2 students, supervised by Professor Changshui Zhang, Dept. of Automation, Tsinghua University </H3>
<UL>
  <LI>Developed a new multi-player game search tree based on a 2-player game tree learnt in class.
</UL>
<H3>8/2009-12/2009 (Embedded Systems) Product Design of Embedded Application with Serial Peripheral Interface</H3>
<H3>Independent, supervised by Professor John Peatman, Dept. of ECE, Georgia Institute of Technology</H3>
<UL>
  <LI>Designed a device to measure the initial height of a free fall by timing the duration of weightlessness.  
  <LI>Developed voltage supply, physical connection and microcontroller program to integrate an accelerometer.
  </UL>
<H3>5/2009-6/2009 (Software Engineering) Object-Oriented Application in Java</H3>
<H3>Independent, supervised by Professor Li Zheng, Dept. of Computer Science, Tsinghua University  </H3>
<UL>
  <LI>Developed a vocabulary building program that features custom-set forgetting curve specified for every word.  
  <LI>Greatly improved my efficiency in vocabulary preparation for GRE test.
  </UL>
<H3>2/2009-6/2009 (Data Structure) k-d Search Tree for Dense Two-Dimensional Data</H3>
<H3>Independent, supervised by Professor Junhui Deng, Dept. of Computer Science, Tsinghua University </H3>
<UL>
  <LI>Developed a k-d tree with modification on tree depth limit and an additional box shrink strategy for scalability.  
  <LI>Ranked top in an in-class competition for algorithm runtime.      
  </UL>
